#
Dolivo Dobrowolski (Von) (M.). — Kraftübertragung mittels Wechselströmen von verschiedener Phase (Drehstrom)
(((English version released ?April? ?May? 1891)))
*

__________________







__________________


📰👨‍💼📰🧙
ALTERNATING CURRENT MOTORS
by⠀
Electrical Review (London)
March 6th, 1891 Page number(s): 291
Vol. XXVIII - Jan 2 to Jun 26 - No. 693

