TESLA'S FLASHES STARTLING But He Won’t Tell What He Is Trying For at Wardencliffe
🐇
'''Some day, but not at this time, I shall make an announcement of something that I never once dreamed of.'''








    ⚡ ⚡ ⚡ ⚡ ⚡ ‘0️⃣4️⃣ ⚡ ⚡ ⚡ ⚡ '04
