UNSUBS --- EQUIPMENT, EXPERIMENTS AND RESEARCH OF NIKOLA TESLA, DECEASED, redactedX ESPIONAGE – M.   RETEL UNDER ABOVE HEADING TO THE BUREAU FROM THIS OFFICE DATED JAN NINE LAST.   INQUIRY DEVELOPS THAT TESLA DIED JAN EIGHT, RATHER THAN THURSDAY, JAN SEVEN, AS sREDACTEDx  STATED IN REFERENCE TELETYPE.   ON THE NIGHT OF JAN EIGHT, SAVxKOSANOVICH, GEORGE CLARK, AND KENNETH SWEEZY VISITED TESLA-S HOTEL WITH A REPRESENTATIVE OF SHAW WALKER CO. IN ORDER TO OPEN THE SAFE IN THE ROOM OF TESLA.  KOSANOVICH LATER REPORTED TO WALTER GORUCH, OFFICE OF ALIEN PROPERTY CUSTODIAN, NYC, THAT HE WENT INTO THE ROOM IN ORDER TO SEARCH FOR A WILL OF TESLA.   KOSANOVICH AND THE OTHERS MADE THE SEARCH OF THE SAFE IN THE PRESENCE OF THREE ASST MANAGERS OF HOTEL NEW YORKER AS WELL AS REPRESENTATIVES OF THE YUGOSLAVIAN CONSULATE, IDENTITIES OF LATTER NOT YET KNOWN.   AFTER THE SAFE WAS OPENED, SEEZEY, TOOK FROM THE SAFE A BOOK CONTAINING TESTIMONIALS SENT TO TESLA ON THE OCCASION OF HIS SEVENTY FIFTH BIRTHDAY.   THIS BOOK WAS ARRANGED FOR TESLA ON THE OCCASION OF HIS SEVENTY FIFTH BIRTHDAY.   THIS BOOK WAS ARRANGED FOR TESLA BY SWEEZEY.   KOSANOVICH TOOK FROM THE ROOM THREE PICTURES OF TESLA, TWO BEING ENLARGED NEWSPAPER PICTUREX[sic].   ACCORDING TO MANAGERS OF HOTEL AND KOSANOVICH HIMSELF, NOTHING ELSE WAS REMOVED FROM THE ROOM OR SAFE.   THE SAFE WAS THEN CLOSED UNDER A NEW COMBINATION, WHICH COMBINATION IS NOW IN POSSESSION OredactedX KOSANOVICH.   ON SATURDAY AFTERNOON, JAN NINE, x GORSUCH AND redactedX FTIZGERALD[sic] OF ALIEN PROPERTY CONTROL WENT TO THE MANHATTAN STORAGE AND WAREHOUSE CO. NY, WHERE THEY ARE NOW LOCATED.  AT THAT redacted TIME THERE WERE ALSO IN THIS WAREHOUSE APPROXIMATELY THIRTY BARRELS AND BUNDLES BELONGING TO TESLA WHICH HAD BEEN THERE SINCE ABOUT NINETEEN THIRTY FOUR.   THESE HAVE ALSO redactedX BEEN SEALED AND ARE NOW UNDER ORDERES OF ALIEN PROPERTYCUSTODIAN[sic].   IN VIEW OF FACT TESLA IS A US NATURALIZED CITIZEN, ALIEN PROPERTY FEELS THAT ITS JURISDICTION OVERY PROPERTY IS DOUBTFUL BUT redactedX FEELS THAT NO OTHER AGENCY WILL BE ABLE TO GET redactedX TO THIS PROPERTY FOR AT LEAST TWO DAYS.

