This text has been entered by John R.H. Penner from a small booklet found in a used bookstore for $2.5 
It seems that some of the sentences, appearing in The Strange Life of Nikola Tesla, have been left out from My Inventions IIIIII. And vice versa, some of the sentences have been added to My Inventions IV
      In the interest of making this important text avalilable to the wider public, he has retyped 
  the entire text word-for-word as it originally appears into this electronic format.
            He has exactly maintained page numbers as they appear in the original – including the 
        somewhat odd artifact of Chapter 11 starting on page 12.
but was indeed the work of divine power At this time, as at many other times in the past, my thoughts turned towards my Mother's teaching. The gift of mental power comes from God, Divine Being, and if we concentrate our minds on that truth, we become in tune with this great power. My Mother had taught me to seek all truth in the Bible; therefore I devoted the next few months to the study of this work. after a short visit to my friends in Watford. At this time I made a further careful study of the Bible, and discovered the key in Revelation. 🐇 100,000,000 volts — one hundred million volts —over 100,000,000 1,000,000 4,000,000 because few indeed, will admit the reality – that God made man in His image – in which case all earth men are alike. There is in fact but one race, of many colours. Christ is but one person, yet he is of all people, so why do some people think themselves better than some other people? aggrandisement aggravatedtho (he missed the ✳️s tho!)
✳️devoid of sustaining planes, ailerons, propellers, and other external✳️
✳️entirely by ✳️reaction✳️
✳️project a missile of this kind into the air and drop it✳️





